HEADWORD: Maturative
<hw>Mat"u*ra*tive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>maturatif</ets>.]</ety> <def>Conducing to ripeness or maturity;
hence, conducing to suppuration.</def>⟦br⟧
